snippet.title: Surviving West -  Trailer
snippet.description:
SURVIVING WEST is a Survival Adventure game. You create your own customized character before you enter a beautilful stylized world. Pick up resources from the ground, craft tools to harvest more resources. Build yourself a house or a castle. Hunt down wild animals for valuable food and resources. Explore the world to find new locations. 

Welcome to SURVIVING WEST - Available on Steam 

Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1563970/West/
Discord:
http://discord.gg/JkUUGbBZE9
